metadata.name: Vision
metadata.description:
Neurons and new beginnings fire in all directions, 
lighting the path ahead of us.

1/1 in the 'Foresight' collection - Description below:

Foresight is unreserved; open to those willing to release and rest.

Through introspection we find hidden crevices on the timeline, allowing us to peak and visualize what lies ahead - for the future is equally as tangible as the present.

Foresight is more than prediction, pattern, patience; rather a vehicle for travel, remembrance, and healing.
